<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>This was originally started within the confines of our Guild forums - and is obviously heavy of characters from within that fold... with that said, you can change the names to whomever you wish within your heads.. if that's what it takes.  I don't consider this to be on par with the writing which Riverdane has demonstrated, but we do what we can..</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
